cts, Antioxidants pharmaceutical products, therapeutic areas satisfying , capsule item and syrup item etc.\n\nAs Subject is registered as a Private Limited Company, it is not required to file financial statements for public review. As such, we are unable to ascertain its present financial health.',2),(4,NULL,NULL,'2023-11-12 20:33:46.808000',NULL,1,'Opinion:','Considering the above-mentioned facts, even though no authentic financial information could be obtained a Credit Limit of USD 156,000.00 has been made.\n\nBased on Subject\'s Score Factor, Subject has been given a credit rating of A.\n\nThe proposed credit line is excellent level.',2);
